---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Zoom! Whitening" 
  category="Cosmetic Dentistry"
  description="Professional teeth whitening with dramatic results in just one hour."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606811841689-23dfddce3e95?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Transform Your Smile in Just One Visit</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Zoom! Whitening is the #1 patient-requested professional whitening treatment. 
        Get noticeably whiter teeth in about an hour while you relax in our comfortable chairs.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Why Choose Zoom! Whitening?
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Fast Results</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">See dramatic whitening results in just one 60-minute session - perfect for busy schedules.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Safe & Proven</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Clinically proven to whiten teeth up to 8 shades with minimal sensitivity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Long-Lasting</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">With proper care, your brighter smile can last for years, not just months.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Comfortable Experience</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Relax in our comfortable chairs while our trained professionals handle everything.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The Zoom! Whitening Process
    </h2>
    
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">1</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Preparation</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">We'll protect your lips and gums, then apply the Zoom! whitening gel to your teeth.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">2</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Activation</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">The Zoom! LED light activates the gel, breaking down stains and discoloration.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">3</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Three 15-Minute Sessions</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">We repeat the process three times for maximum whitening power - you can listen to music or watch TV!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-300 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">4</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Reveal Your New Smile</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">After just one hour, walk out with a noticeably brighter, more confident smile!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">
          Perfect For
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Special events (weddings, graduations)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Coffee and tea drinkers</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Wine enthusiasts</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Anyone wanting immediate results</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">
          Maintain Your Results
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-900 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Use Zoom! take-home touch-up kit</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-900 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Avoid staining foods/drinks for 48 hours</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-900 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Regular dental cleanings</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-900 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Good oral hygiene habits</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">
        Ready for a Brighter Smile?
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Join thousands of satisfied patients who've transformed their smiles with Zoom! Whitening. 
        Book your appointment today and see the difference professional whitening can make.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 italic">
        * Results vary by individual. Most patients see 6-8 shades of improvement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/veneers" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Veneers & Lumineers</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Perfect your smile shape and color</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/invisalign" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Invisalign®</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Straighten teeth discreetly</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/cleanings-exams" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Professional Cleanings</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Maintain your bright smile</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Is Zoom! Whitening safe for my teeth?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Yes! Zoom! is clinically proven safe and effective. The gel contains calcium phosphate which 
        helps protect enamel during the whitening process. Our trained professionals ensure proper 
        application to minimize any sensitivity.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How long do the results last?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        With proper care, Zoom! Whitening results can last 1-3 years. We provide take-home 
        touch-up trays to help maintain your bright smile. Avoiding staining foods and drinks, 
        along with good oral hygiene, will extend your results.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Will I experience sensitivity?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Some patients experience temporary sensitivity during or after treatment. We use desensitizing 
        gel and can adjust the treatment if needed. Most sensitivity resolves within 24-48 hours. 
        We'll provide specific aftercare instructions to minimize any discomfort.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How white will my teeth get?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Most patients see an improvement of 6-8 shades, though results vary based on your starting 
        shade and individual factors. During your consultation, we'll show you expected results 
        using our shade guide so you know what to expect.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>